.top
  = render 'layouts/header'
  .top-contents
    .top-content__main
    .top-content__intoroduction
      %h2{ class: "top-intoroduction-subtitle" } FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
      %ul{ class: "top-intoroduction-lists" }
        %li{ class: "top-intoroduction-list" }
          .top-intoroduction-list__pict
            %span{ class: "top-intoroduction-list__number" } 1
            = image_tag "/assets/pict-reason-01.jpg", class: "banner__main-image"
          %h3{ class:"top-intoroduction-list__text" }
            %span 3分
            ですぐに出品
          %p{ class:"top-intoroduction-list__description" }
            スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
        %li{ class: "top-intoroduction-list" }
          .top-intoroduction-list__pict
            %span{ class: "top-intoroduction-list__number" } 2
            = image_tag "/assets/pict-reason-02.jpg", class: "banner__main-image"
          %h3{ class:"top-intoroduction-list__text" }
            %span シンプル
            で使いやすい
          %p{ class:"top-intoroduction-list__description" }
            めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
        %li{ class: "top-intoroduction-list-last" }
          .top-intoroduction-list__pict
            %span{ class: "top-intoroduction-list__number" } 3
            = image_tag "/assets/pict-reason-03.jpg", class: "banner__main-image"
          %h3{ class:"top-intoroduction-list__text" }
            手数料
            %span 業界最安
          %p{ class:"top-intoroduction-list__description" }
            最大3%でお得に出品&amp;購入！
    .top-content__banner 
    .top-content__futures
      %h2{ class: "top-futures-subtitle" } FURIMAの特徴
      .top-futuers-lists
        .top-futures-list
          .top-futures-list__pict
            = image_tag "/assets/icon-01.png" 
          %h3{ class:"top-futures-list__text" }
            簡単に売り買いできる
          %p{ class:"top-futures-list__description" }
            スマホひとつで、いつでもどこでも簡単に出品・購入が可能！
        .top-futures-list
          .top-futures-list__pict
            = image_tag "/assets/icon-03.png" 
          %h3{ class:"top-futures-list__text" }
            売上金は即日振込みに対応
          %p{ class:"top-futures-list__description" }
            午前9時までに振込を依頼いただければ、翌日に指定の口座に入金いたします!
        .top-futures-list
          .top-futures-list__pict
            = image_tag "/assets/icon-04.png" 
          %h3{ class:"top-futures-list__text" }
            様々な支払いに対応
          %p{ class:"top-futures-list__description" }
            お支払いは、クレジットカードだけでなく、ポイントや売上金など多彩な方法があります。
    .top-content__pickup-items 
    .top-content__pickup-items 
  = render 'layouts/banner'
  = render 'layouts/footer'
